  <brief_title>PERmixon® in LUTS Evaluation Study (PERLES)</brief_title>
  <acronym>PERLES</acronym>
  <official_title>PERMIXON® 160 mg Hard Capsule Versus Placebo in the Treatment of Symptomatic Lower Urinary Tract Symptoms Due to Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Pierre Fabre Medicament</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Pierre Fabre Medicament</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to support the efficacy of Permixon 160 mg b.i.d. in treating
      subjects with symptomatic Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia (BPH), compared to placebo, using
      Tamsulosine LP 0.4 mg as a reference treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
